{
  "stem": "10829.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But they were the first ones that they shot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They put them in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then we'd go, and they would have to get dressed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then we would go, we'd pick up the clothes and put it  down in piles.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And well, this thing went on for about three times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then after a while, when the city was pretty well thinned out, they made another section.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now you were already in a half of the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this was just about coming up to the middle of the town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they-- they also took from one side of the street, and now they put us all on the other side of the street.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we were already up to the shul from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then they took from the other end of the town, they brought everybody towards the middle of the town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we went through that three times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, approximately-- to the best of my knowledge, and from this-- there-- there's a lot of talk about a lot of people in there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think, out of the 12,000, I don't think we have more than 200, 300 people that are alive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of my relatives from my family survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think we had more than two-- I think I would be stretching it like to the end of its teeth if we had 250 people survive Trochenbrod.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only ones that-- we-- we had a lot from the ghettos, we had a lot of survivors.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then we were in the forest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the forest, we used to have the [INAUDIBLE], which is a different story.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
